title: BONUS: Nobody Asked E14: Valentime's Day w/ Ashlee and Her BFF Ryan Cabrera (S1E4 Part Two)
itunes:title: BONUS: Nobody Asked E14: Valentime's Day w/ Ashlee and Her BFF Ryan Cabrera (S1E4 Part Two)
description:
A bonus episode from the Patreon! Did you know Nora McInerny of Terrible, Thanks For Asking and Caroline have a Patreon podcast? It’s called NOBODY ASKED: Revisiting The Early 2000s Reality Shows That Shaped Our Lives. So far we’ve gone back and watched Newlyweds: Nick and Jessica, MTV’s Rich Girls, the first season of American Idol, and now we’re on The Ashlee Simpson Show. We have no plans to stop, so don’t even try to stop us! We will do this until every show has been watched and every pair of our pants has been peed in from laughing so hard.


For $4.99/month you get access to all of our NOBODY ASKED episodes, which will land right in your podcast feeds with no extra work from you. You’ll also get lots of bonus content like pictures of Nora wearing an Old Navy blazer to concerts.


You can subscribe here and we would LOVE TO HAVE YOU!!: https://www.patreon.com/geethanksandfriends 


It's Valentime's Day and Ashlee is hanging out with her "best friend" Ryan Cabrera who she makes out with (she says this is normal). Plus, Caroline pees her pants. Plus, people with moderate to severe plaque psoriasis are rethinking their choices??? Plus, Ashlee's friend wears low rise ballet tights to ballet class. Also, TIna goes to Ryan's concert? Why? ...like, really, why? Tina get a life you freak!




Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
